{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/architecture/programming101-4/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jaehyeon's Dev Blog","author":"Jaehyeon Kim","siteUrl":"https://jaehyeon48.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"jaehyeon48/blog-comments"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"94776495-f70c-5f0b-8f54-c06a3034d65d","excerpt":"이 글은 최범균님의 프로그래밍 초식 시리즈을 요약한 글입니다. If…","html":"<p>이 글은 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRdML08R2Yo&#x26;list=PLwouWTPuIjUg0dmHoxgqNXyx3Acy7BNCz\">최범균님의 프로그래밍 초식 시리즈</a>을 요약한 글입니다.</p>\n<hr class=\"custom-hr\">\n<h2 id=\"if-조건-역으로-바꾸기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#if-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4-%EC%97%AD%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%94%EA%BE%B8%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"if 조건 역으로 바꾸기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>If 조건 역으로 바꾸기</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건이 많거나, 중첩된 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건이 많아지면 코드가 복잡해지고 분석하기 어려워진다. <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건을 덜 복잡하게 하는 여러 방법들 중 가장 쉬운(?) 방법을 살펴보자.</p>\n<h3 id=\"흔한-요구사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%9D%94%ED%95%9C-%EC%9A%94%EA%B5%AC%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"흔한 요구사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>흔한 요구사항</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">A</code>인 경우에만 <code class=\"language-text\">E</code>를 실행한다:</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">A</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// E 실행</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">A</code>인 경우에, 그리고 <code class=\"language-text\">B</code>인 경우에는 <code class=\"language-text\">E</code>를 실행한다:</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">A</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// B 조건을 구함</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">B</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// E 실행</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>하지만, 다음 그림과 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 블록이 길어지게 되면 모니터 한 화면에 안 들어오게 되고 스크롤을 해야 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 블록의 끝을 알 수 있다. 또한, 코드를 분석할 때 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 블록의 실행 조건을 머릿속에 기억하면서 코드를 분석해 나가야 한다:</p>\n<figure>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jaehyeon48/jaehyeon48.github.io@master/assets/images/web/programming101/too_long_if_block.png\" alt=\"너무 긴 if 블록\">\n    <figcaption>출처: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z4qE_IfSrD4&amp;list=PLwouWTPuIjUg0dmHoxgqNXyx3Acy7BNCz&amp;index=7</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h3 id=\"코드-구조가-이렇다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EA%B0%80-%EC%9D%B4%EB%A0%87%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"코드 구조가 이렇다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>코드 구조가 이렇다면?</h3>\n<p>아래 코드들과 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">else</code> 가 없거나, <code class=\"language-text\">else</code> 로직이 단순한 경우가 종종 있다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> </code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    logger<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'some message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">A</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// B 조건 구함</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">B</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// E 실행</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이러한 코드들은 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건을 역으로 바꿈으로써 코드를 좀 더 단순화할 수 있다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* NOT GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* NOT GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    logger<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'some message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">someFunc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>someCondition<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    logger<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'some message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 많은 코드</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* NOT GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">A</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// B 조건 구함</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">B</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// E 실행</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* GOOD */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token constant\">A</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// B조건 구함</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token constant\">B</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// E 실행</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"if-조건을-역으로-바꾸게-되면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#if-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%84-%EC%97%AD%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B0%94%EA%BE%B8%EA%B2%8C-%EB%90%98%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"if 조건을 역으로 바꾸게 되면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>If 조건을 역으로 바꾸게 되면…</h2>\n<p>위 사례들과 같이, <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건을 역으로 바꾸게 되면 <code class=\"language-text\">else</code> 가 없다는 사실을 빨리 파악할 수 있다. 또한, <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 조건을 기억해야 할 범위가 좁아져서 상대적으로 인지 부하가 감소되고, 인덴트의 깊이가 줄어들어 코드가 간결해진다. 따라서 그만큼 코드 분석에 좀 더 유리해진다고 할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>물론 <code class=\"language-text\">if-else</code> 문을 써야하는 경우도 있겠지만..(어디에나 예외는 있으니 말이다) 되도록이면 <strong>early return</strong> 패턴을 적용해서 인덴트의 깊이를 줄이고, <code class=\"language-text\">if</code> 블록의 길이를 줄여 코드를 더 깔끔하게 작성하는 편이 좋을 것 같다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"프로그래밍 초식 요약 - Early return","date":"December 08, 2021","category":"architecture"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/architecture/programming101-4/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/architecture/programming101-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"프로그래밍 초식 요약 - 변수 아끼기"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/architecture/programming101-3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"프로그래밍 초식 요약 - What? How?"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}